    <div id="tswcontainer">
      <div id="tswheader">
        <!-- start of header section: insert your logo, etc, here -->
        <h1 style="text-align: center;">Inverse Polarity - Resources</h1>
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <!-- end of header section: insert your logo, etc, above this line --> </div>
      <div id="tswcontent">Hi, I'm Ashley and this is a website with information
        on the Minecraft mod I have made themed around the robotics team:
        Inverse Polarity.<br>
        <div>
          <p>It is a decently sized mod, adding around 80 blocks/items as of
            1.3. It is required on both the server and client side and does
            impact world generation.</p>
          <p>As you may be able to tell from the changelogs, I have made many
            major mistakes, such as forgetting to add the crafting recipes for
            the armor until 1.3 (the armor was added in 1.0).</p>
          <p>This mod was originally made using Fabric 1.20.1, but I have ported
            it to 1.20.4(probably temporary) and 1.21.1. I plan to support newer
            versions in the future.</p>
          <p>Some features of this mod rely on 1.20 content, so I don't plan on
            porting it before then, and I don't plan on porting to forge or
            neoforge as of now.</p>
          <p>Anyways, I hope you enjoy the mod, and I hope you find this
            information useful.</p>
          <p><br>
          </p>
